{
  "id": "RAW_0aa3d7",
  "title": "高效部署通义万相 Wan2.1：ComfyUI 文生/图生视频实战，工作流直取！",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/94_PO1rAAIlPcyRvXy6YGA",
  "date": "2025-03-03 13:02:20",
  "author": "魔搭开发者",
  "siteName": "魔搭ModelScope社区",
  "content": "\n \n \n  <article data-identifier-application__slash__x-doc-key=\"Pd6l24LXXMa2q7Ma\">\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkxNTM5NTg2OA==&amp;mid=2247501176&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=5105a4f9db9b56ecb978361c2f58357e&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"通义万相Wan2.1开源\" linktype=\"text\" imgurl=\"\" imgdata=\"null\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" tab=\"innerlink\" data-linktype=\"2\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">通义万相Wan2.1开源</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">不到一周，已登顶HuggingFace&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Model 和 Space 榜双榜首，在HuggingFace和ModelScope平台的累计下载量突破100万次，社区热度持续攀升！为响应<span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: left;\">小伙伴们</span>对ComfyUI工作流运行<span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: left;\">W</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: left;\">an2.</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: left;\">1</span>的强烈需求，<span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: left;\">社区开发者整理了实战教程👇&nbsp;</span></span><br></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><br></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">本文将手把手教你分别在魔搭免费GPU算力环境、本地环境部署</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">运行ComfyUI工作流，玩转W</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">an2.</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">1文生视频、图生视频案例实践。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br></p>\n   <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;margin:10px auto;outline:0px;visibility:visible;display:flex;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;justify-content:center;\">\n    <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding-bottom: 3px;outline: 0px;border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(6, 84, 234);transform: skew(-10deg);visibility: visible;\">\n     <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;\">\n      <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding: 5px 18px;outline: 0px;display: flex;align-items: center;transform: skew(10deg);visibility: visible;\">\n       <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;transform-style: preserve-3d;visibility: visible;\">\n        <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;color: rgb(6, 84, 234);transform: translateZ(10px);text-align: left;visibility: visible;\">\n         <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-weight: bolder;visibility: visible;font-size: 17px;\">01</span>\n        </section>\n       </section>\n       <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding-left: 18px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(6, 84, 234);text-align: left;visibility: visible;\">\n        <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-weight: bolder;visibility: visible;font-size: 17px;\">魔搭Notebook运行ComfyUI文生视频工作流</span>\n       </section>\n       <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 18px;font-weight: bolder;visibility: visible;\"><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"></span></p>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;text-align: left;visibility: visible;\"><br></p>\n   <h3 style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 82, 255);\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 82, 255);font-size: 17px;\">step1&nbsp; 如何在魔搭中启动Notebook</span></strong></span></h3>\n   <p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 82, 255);\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 82, 255);font-size: 17px;\"><br></span></strong></span></p>\n   <h4 style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">1、打开</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">ModelScope 魔搭社区</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">首页，点击我的Notebook</span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"></span></strong></h4>\n   <h4 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"></span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><br data-path=\"5,3\"></span><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100017620\" data-ratio=\"0.4703703703703704\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/cd5412b1-07c8-475c-331f-a4ad1acabb00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width:518px;height:244px;opacity:1;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/cd5412b1-07c8-475c-331f-a4ad1acabb00/public\"></h4>\n   <h4 style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">2、魔搭社区免费提供的GPU免费算力上体验，选择方式二启动后点击查看Notebook</span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"></span></strong></h4>\n   <p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><br></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100017618\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e0b27897-279b-4b53-e602-809bc2a1f700/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width:260px;height:130px;opacity:1;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e0b27897-279b-4b53-e602-809bc2a1f700/public\">&nbsp; &nbsp;<img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100017619\" data-ratio=\"0.5046296296296297\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8bd517eb-f9af-4d84-57b4-e8dee5987e00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width:258px;height:130.209375px;opacity:1;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8bd517eb-f9af-4d84-57b4-e8dee5987e00/public\"></p>\n   <p><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><br></span></p>\n   <h3 style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 82, 255);\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 82, 255);font-size: 17px;\">step2&nbsp; 安装ComfyUI及其依赖</span></strong></span></h3>\n   <h4 style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">1、打开Notebook终端</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"></span></strong></h4>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在页面中选择Terminal</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100017617\" data-ratio=\"0.6222222222222222\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/cc7f9ed9-2d04-4cfc-c762-085980f31e00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width:689px;height:428.47187500000007px;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/cc7f9ed9-2d04-4cfc-c762-085980f31e00/public\"></p>\n   <h4 style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">2、克隆ComfyUI仓库</span></strong></h4>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在Notebook终端中运行如下命令，将官方的ComfyUI的仓库克隆下来：</span></p>\n   <section class=\"code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js\">\n    <ul class=\"code-snippet__line-index code-snippet__js\">\n     <li></li>\n    </ul>\n    <pre class=\"code-snippet__js\" data-lang=\"php\"><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">  git <span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">clone</span> https:<span class=\"code-snippet__comment\">//github.com/comfyanonymous/ComfyUI.git</span></span></code></pre>\n   </section>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100017616\" data-ratio=\"0.12962962962962962\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/3250f70d-1030-4a07-61a7-fbf7b2c1ac00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width:689px;height:89.20468557336622px;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/3250f70d-1030-4a07-61a7-fbf7b2c1ac00/public\"></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><br></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">克隆过程中可能遇到这个报错，提示“RPC失败”：</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100017624\" data-ratio=\"0.18518518518518517\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/379e9d0a-3121-418d-c7c1-815aea1ec400/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width:689px;height:127.90841584158416px;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/379e9d0a-3121-418d-c7c1-815aea1ec400/public\"></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><br></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">这是因为http协议版本的问题导致网络连接失败，版本降低至1.1即可解决。命令如下：</span></p>\n   <section class=\"code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js\">\n    <ul class=\"code-snippet__line-index code-snippet__js\">\n     <li></li>\n     <li></li>\n     <li></li>\n    </ul>\n    <pre class=\"code-snippet__js\" data-lang=\"php\"><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">  git config --<span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">global</span> http.version HTTP/<span class=\"code-snippet__number\">1.1</span></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">  git <span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">clone</span> https:<span class=\"code-snippet__comment\">//github.com/comfyanonymous/ComfyUI.git</span></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">  git config --<span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">global</span> http.version HTTP/<span class=\"code-snippet__number\">2</span></span></code></pre>\n   </section>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><br></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">完成的界面像这样：</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100017622\" data-ratio=\"0.1648148148148148\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/6b38aca7-5f43-450a-63a5-15453f9b1300/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width:689px;height:113.42260442260442px;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/6b38aca7-5f43-450a-63a5-15453f9b1300/public\"></p>\n   <h4 style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">3、安装依赖</span></strong></h4>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">使用pip安装运行ComfyUI服务所需的环境依赖：</span></p>\n   <section class=\"code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js\">\n    <ul class=\"code-snippet__line-index code-snippet__js\">\n     <li></li>\n     <li></li>\n    </ul>\n    <pre class=\"code-snippet__js\" data-lang=\"properties\"><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><span class=\"code-snippet__attr\">cd</span> <span class=\"code-snippet__string\">ComfyUI</span></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><span class=\"code-snippet__attr\">pip</span> <span class=\"code-snippet__string\">install -r requirements.txt</span></span></code></pre>\n   </section>\n   <h4 style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">4、验证安装</span></strong></h4>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">运行以下命令启动ComfyUI服务，测试是否成功安装。</span></p>\n   <section class=\"code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js\">\n    <ul class=\"code-snippet__line-index code-snippet__js\">\n     <li></li>\n    </ul>\n    <pre class=\"code-snippet__js\" data-lang=\"css\"><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><span class=\"code-snippet__selector-tag\">python</span> <span class=\"code-snippet__selector-tag\">main</span><span class=\"code-snippet__selector-class\">.py</span></span></code></pre>\n   </section>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><br></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">如果服务成功启动，将在终端中看到http://127.0.0.1:8188的提示</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100017623\" data-ratio=\"0.24166666666666667\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f4bd7f84-1758-464f-c343-f5051ec7b800/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width:100%;height:516px;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f4bd7f84-1758-464f-c343-f5051ec7b800/public\"></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><br></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">点击这个链接就可以进入comfyui的界面啦！</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><br></span></p>\n   <h3 style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 17px;color: rgb(0, 82, 255);\">step3&nbsp; 文生视频工作流</span></strong></h3>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">以通义万相wan2.1-t2v-1.3b文生视频模型为例，演示如何运行工作流。</span></p>\n   <h4 style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">1、下载模型</span></strong></h4>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">wan2.1-t2v-1.3b文生视频模型包含3个组件，文本编码器、扩散模型和视频解码器。我们需要从</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">魔搭模型库</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">中下载3个组件对应的模型文件，并将这些模型文件放置到对应文件夹：</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><br></span></p>\n   <ul class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"font-size: 15px;\">\n     <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">文本编码器：</span></p></li>\n    <ul class=\"list-paddingleft-1\" style=\"list-style-type: square;\">\n     <li style=\"font-size: 15px;\">\n      <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">split_files/text_encoders/umt5_xxl_fp16.safetensors →ComfyUI/models/text_encoders</span></p></li>\n    </ul>\n    <li style=\"font-size: 15px;\">\n     <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">扩散模型</span></p></li>\n    <ul class=\"list-paddingleft-1\" style=\"list-style-type: square;\">\n     <li style=\"font-size: 15px;\">\n      <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">split_files/diffusion_models/wan2.1_t2v_1.3B_bf16.safetensors → ComfyUI/models/diffusion_models</span></p></li>\n    </ul>\n    <li style=\"font-size: 15px;\">\n     <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">视频解码器</span></p></li>\n    <ul class=\"list-paddingleft-1\" style=\"list-style-type: square;\">\n     <li style=\"font-size: 15px;\">\n      <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">split_files/vae/wan_2.1_vae.safetensors → ComfyUI/models/vae</span></p></li>\n    </ul>\n   </ul>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><br></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">命令行如下：</span></p>\n   <section class=\"code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js\">\n    <ul class=\"code-snippet__line-index code-snippet__js\">\n     <li></li>\n     <li></li>\n     <li></li>\n     <li></li>\n     <li></li>\n     <li></li>\n    </ul>\n    <pre class=\"code-snippet__js\" data-lang=\"php\"><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><span class=\"code-snippet__comment\"># 文本编码器</span></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">modelscope download --model Comfy-Org/Wan_2<span class=\"code-snippet__number\">.1</span>_ComfyUI_repackaged --<span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">include</span> split_files/text_encoders/umt5_xxl_fp16.safetensors --local_dir ./models/text_encoders/</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><span class=\"code-snippet__comment\"># 扩散模型</span></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">modelscope download --model Comfy-Org/Wan_2<span class=\"code-snippet__number\">.1</span>_ComfyUI_repackaged --<span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">include</span> split_files/diffusion_models/wan2<span class=\"code-snippet__number\">.1</span>_t2v_1<span class=\"code-snippet__number\">.3</span>B_bf16.safetensors --local_dir ./models/diffusion_models/</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><span class=\"code-snippet__comment\"># 视频解码器</span></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">modelscope&nbsp;download&nbsp;--model&nbsp;Comfy-Org/Wan_2<span class=\"code-snippet__number\">.1</span>_ComfyUI_repackaged&nbsp;--<span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">include</span>&nbsp;split_files/vae/wan_2<span class=\"code-snippet__number\">.1</span>_vae.safetensors&nbsp;--local_dir&nbsp;./models/vae/</span></code></pre>\n   </section>\n   <pre style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><br></span></pre>\n   <h4 style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">2、启动comfyui</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"></span></h4>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">运行以下命令启动ComfyUI服务：</span></p>\n   <section class=\"code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js\">\n    <ul class=\"code-snippet__line-index code-snippet__js\">\n     <li></li>\n    </ul>\n    <pre class=\"code-snippet__js\" data-lang=\"css\"><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><span class=\"code-snippet__selector-tag\">python</span> <span class=\"code-snippet__selector-tag\">main</span><span class=\"code-snippet__selector-class\">.py</span></span></code></pre>\n   </section>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100017625\" data-ratio=\"0.24166666666666667\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f4bd7f84-1758-464f-c343-f5051ec7b800/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width:100%;height:516px;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f4bd7f84-1758-464f-c343-f5051ec7b800/public\"></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><br></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">点击http://127.0.0.1:8188链接进入comfyui的界面</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><br></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100017626\" data-ratio=\"0.6185185185185185\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/13ca0461-63ea-48af-db12-ceff06e77a00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width:445px;height:275.1077885952712px;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/13ca0461-63ea-48af-db12-ceff06e77a00/public\"></p>\n   <h4 style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">3、运行文生视频工作流</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"></span></h4>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">ComfyUI启动后会自动打开一个默认的工作流，可以不用管它。我们需要下载wan2.1的示例工作流文件，然后将文件拖入ComfyUI界面。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><br></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">wan2.1的示例工作流文件：</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">https://modelscope.cn/notebook/share/ipynb/5eee8a46/text_to_video_wan.ipynb</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><br></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">拖入后在界面中就可以看到工作流的样子，分别点击三个模型的下拉选项，检查一下模型文件是否存在，再点击“执行”开始视频生成。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><br></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100017630\" data-ratio=\"0.5592592592592592\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/6c4cd694-21c7-4f03-616a-6a1b2e956500/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width:100%;height:1774px;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/6c4cd694-21c7-4f03-616a-6a1b2e956500/public\"></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><br></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">视频生成完成之后的页面：</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100017631\" data-ratio=\"0.512962962962963\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/ac9b9b80-f4c2-4ea2-49db-d62147a1fe00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width:772px;height:396px;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/ac9b9b80-f4c2-4ea2-49db-d62147a1fe00/public\"></p>\n   <h4 style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">4、运行日志查看</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"></span></h4>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">终端界面上可以查看实时运行的日志：</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><br></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100017629\" data-ratio=\"0.25925925925925924\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f52e25a5-fcd1-4689-eaef-74d47c607500/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width:445px;height:115.19073569482288px;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f52e25a5-fcd1-4689-eaef-74d47c607500/public\"></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><br></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">nvidia-smi命令可以查看显存占用：</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><br></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100017628\" data-ratio=\"0.46944444444444444\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/3bedf7d0-06d1-4112-e61e-f7a7df8a2d00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width:445px;height:209.04651162790697px;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/3bedf7d0-06d1-4112-e61e-f7a7df8a2d00/public\"></p>\n   <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;margin:10px auto;outline:0px;visibility:visible;display:flex;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;justify-content:center;\">\n    <section style=\"padding-bottom: 3px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(6, 84, 234);transform: skew(-10deg);visibility: visible;\">\n     <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;\">\n      <section style=\"padding: 5px 18px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;display: flex;align-items: center;transform: skew(10deg);visibility: visible;\">\n       <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;transform-style: preserve-3d;visibility: visible;\">\n        <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;color: rgb(6, 84, 234);transform: translateZ(10px);text-align: left;visibility: visible;\">\n         <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-weight: bolder;visibility: visible;font-size: 17px;\">02</span>\n        </section>\n       </section>\n       <section style=\"padding-left: 18px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(6, 84, 234);text-align: left;visibility: visible;\">\n        <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-weight: bolder;visibility: visible;font-size: 17px;\">本地搭建ComfyUI图生视频工作流</span>\n       </section>\n       <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 18px;font-weight: bolder;visibility: visible;\"><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"></span></p>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;text-align: left;visibility: visible;\"><br></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">如果你自己拥有GPU，则可以选择在本地部署工作流。本节以通义万相wan2.1-i2v-14b的图生视频模型为例，教你一步步用命令行运行图生视频的工作流。</span></p>\n   <h3 style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px;color: rgb(0, 82, 255);\"><strong>step1&nbsp; 检查显卡信息</strong></span></h3>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">要运行万相wan2.1-i2v-14b文生视频ComfyUI工作流，需要高规格的显卡。生成512*512大小的视频，显存大约需要44G；生成1280*720尺寸的视频，显存需要53GB。运行nvidia-smi命令，检查显卡是否符合要求。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><br></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100017627\" data-ratio=\"0.4287037037037037\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/784fc031-11f1-4808-ac0e-264ae748e500/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width:545px;height:233.67911479944675px;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/784fc031-11f1-4808-ac0e-264ae748e500/public\"></p>\n   <h3 style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 82, 255);\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 82, 255);font-size: 17px;\">step2&nbsp; 安装ComfyUI及其依赖</span></strong></span></h3>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">此步骤同上，请查阅上一节step2。</span></p>\n   <h3 style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 82, 255);\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 82, 255);font-size: 17px;\">step3&nbsp; 图生视频工作流</span></strong></span></h3>\n   <h4 style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">1、模型下载</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"></span></h4>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">wan2.1-i2v-1.3b文生视频模型包含4个组件，图片编码器、文本编码器、视频扩散模型和视频解码器。我们需要从</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">魔搭模型库</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">中下载4个组件对应的模型文件，并将这些模型文件放置到对应文件夹：</span></p>\n   <ul class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"font-size: 15px;\">\n     <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">图片编码器</span></p></li>\n    <ul class=\"list-paddingleft-1\" style=\"list-style-type: square;\">\n     <li style=\"font-size: 15px;\">\n      <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">split_files/clip_vision/clip_vision_h.safetensors →ComfyUI/models/clip_vision</span></p></li>\n    </ul>\n    <li style=\"font-size: 15px;\">\n     <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">文本编码器</span></p></li>\n    <ul class=\"list-paddingleft-1\" style=\"list-style-type: square;\">\n     <li style=\"font-size: 15px;\">\n      <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">split_files/text_encoders/umt5_xxl_fp16.safetensors →ComfyUI/models/text_encoders</span></p></li>\n    </ul>\n    <li style=\"font-size: 15px;\">\n     <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">视频扩散模型</span></p></li>\n    <ul class=\"list-paddingleft-1\" style=\"list-style-type: square;\">\n     <li style=\"font-size: 15px;\">\n      <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">split_files/diffusion_models/wan2.1_i2v_720p_14B_bf16.safetensors → ComfyUI/models/diffusion_models</span></p></li>\n    </ul>\n    <li style=\"font-size: 15px;\">\n     <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">视频解码器</span></p></li>\n    <ul class=\"list-paddingleft-1\" style=\"list-style-type: square;\">\n     <li style=\"font-size: 15px;\">\n      <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">split_files/vae/wan_2.1_vae.safetensors → ComfyUI/models/vae</span></p></li>\n    </ul>\n   </ul>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><br></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">命令行如下：</span></p>\n   <section class=\"code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js\">\n    <ul class=\"code-snippet__line-index code-snippet__js\">\n     <li></li>\n     <li></li>\n     <li></li>\n     <li></li>\n     <li></li>\n     <li></li>\n     <li></li>\n     <li></li>\n    </ul>\n    <pre class=\"code-snippet__js\" data-lang=\"php\"><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><span class=\"code-snippet__comment\"># 图片编码器</span></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">modelscope download --model Comfy-Org/Wan_2<span class=\"code-snippet__number\">.1</span>_ComfyUI_repackaged --<span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">include</span> split_files/clip_vision/clip_vision_h.safetensors --local_dir ./models/clip_vision/</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><span class=\"code-snippet__comment\"># 文本编码器</span></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">modelscope download --model Comfy-Org/Wan_2<span class=\"code-snippet__number\">.1</span>_ComfyUI_repackaged --<span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">include</span> split_files/text_encoders/umt5_xxl_fp16.safetensors --local_dir ./models/text_encoders/</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><span class=\"code-snippet__comment\"># 视频扩散模型</span></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">modelscope download --model Comfy-Org/Wan_2<span class=\"code-snippet__number\">.1</span>_ComfyUI_repackaged --<span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">include</span> split_files/diffusion_models/wan2<span class=\"code-snippet__number\">.1</span>_i2v_720p_14B_bf16.safetensors --local_dir ./models/diffusion_models/</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><span class=\"code-snippet__comment\"># 视频解码器</span></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">modelscope&nbsp;download&nbsp;--model&nbsp;Comfy-Org/Wan_2<span class=\"code-snippet__number\">.1</span>_ComfyUI_repackaged&nbsp;--<span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">include</span>&nbsp;split_files/vae/wan_2<span class=\"code-snippet__number\">.1</span>_vae.safetensors&nbsp;--local_dir&nbsp;./models/vae/</span></code></pre>\n   </section>\n   <pre style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><br></span></pre>\n   <h4 style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">2、启动comfyui</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"></span></h4>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">运行以下命令启动ComfyUI服务：</span></p>\n   <section class=\"code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js\">\n    <ul class=\"code-snippet__line-index code-snippet__js\">\n     <li></li>\n    </ul>\n    <pre class=\"code-snippet__js\" data-lang=\"css\"><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><span class=\"code-snippet__selector-tag\">python</span> <span class=\"code-snippet__selector-tag\">main</span><span class=\"code-snippet__selector-class\">.py</span></span></code></pre>\n   </section>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100017632\" data-ratio=\"0.24166666666666667\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f4bd7f84-1758-464f-c343-f5051ec7b800/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width:100%;height:516px;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f4bd7f84-1758-464f-c343-f5051ec7b800/public\"></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><br></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">点击http://127.0.0.1:8188链接就可以进入comfyui的界面</span></p>\n   <h4 style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">3、上传工作流运行</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"></span></h4>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">下载wan2.1的图生视频示例工作流文件，然后将文件拖入ComfyUI界面。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><br></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">wan2.1的示例工作流文件：</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">https://modelscope.cn/notebook/share/ipynb/0e5bbc8b/image_to_video_wan_example.ipynb</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><br></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">拖入后在界面中就可以看到工作流的样子，分别点击三个模型的下拉选项，检查一下模型文件是否存在，再点击“执行”开始视频生成。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><br></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100017633\" data-ratio=\"0.5731481481481482\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/a2c52b14-d645-4f45-8538-3cdc002a1800/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width:751px;height:431px;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/a2c52b14-d645-4f45-8538-3cdc002a1800/public\"></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br></p>\n  </article>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"10000\"></mp-style-type></p>\n \n",
